The best explanation I can give is through this conversation I had with Reach. Note that the following can be considered spoilers, but shouldn't be considered the truth of what's going on in this article.

+block

–block


 I started thinking, by the way, that the friggin' attic didn't even exist.

 Good.

 Let me background a bit

 Go fer it!

 I had a brother who died when I was little. He was a newborn, but he didn't make it.

 Really shook the family up

 I didn't handle it well at the time

 and even though I never met him, I kept seeing him everywhere

 anyway

 in the dream, he's in the attic.

 And I dont realize it until the very end

 but then I find that he never existed

 So, yeah.

 That's basically what's going on here.




Anyway, many thanks to Reach, TwistedGears, Roget, and others who looked at this. It feels good to write this one, I hope you guys like it.

As usual, your comments, critiques and criticisms are always welcome.







